        <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">polymorphisms</ENAMEX> listed in <ENAMEX TYPE="PRODUCT">Table 1are</ENAMEX> provided in the
        additional file <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">1</NUMEX>. The genomewide screen for a large number
