        polymorphisms with <ENAMEX TYPE="DISEASE">cerebrovascular disease</ENAMEX> and <ENAMEX TYPE="DISEASE">stroke</ENAMEX> in
        sickle cell disease. <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">DNA samples</ENAMEX> will be pooled in the <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">230</NUMEX>
